Installation Instructions
=========================

NOTE: stratagus ( http://stratagus.sourceforge.net ) is required.
wargus and stratagus version must match
(same version or CVS from the same date)

NOTE: 

Windows:
1. extract data: 'build.bat /path/to/cd [ /path/to/outputdir ]'
    eg: build.bat d:\

2. start stratagus: '/path/to/stratagus -d /path/to/outputdir'
    eg: c:\stratagus\stratagus.exe -d data.wc2

Unix:
1. extract data: './build.sh -p /path/to/cd [ -o /path/to/outputdir ]'
    eg: ./build.sh -p /cdrom

2. start stratagus: 'stratagus -d data.wc2'
